{"tid":2146151,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"鄭若驊回應被制裁　稱有國家作強大後盾不會被嚇倒","createTime":"2020-08-08T11:41:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-08T17:44:55.000Z","uid":66324,"like":33,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":47,"replies":[{"pid":"d783640f693d3257fa742c9b37546349c271c838","tid":2146151,"uid":66324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T11:41:54.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1542602-20200808.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1542602-20200808.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=Ieu1u4uPL9fG%2BDPeYXLiW4eNTHq1rgEicHo%2BkVhR8rs%3D&h=8a0b1bd2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1542602-20200808.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=b0534597\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1542602-20200808.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n律政司司長鄭若驊回應被美國財政部列入制裁名單，表示美方以絕望和非法的制裁手法，進一步加強了她認為自己一直處事正確的信念，又說有國家作為強大後盾，她不會被嚇倒，美國所謂的制裁行動是徒勞無功。<br />\n<br />\n本台就鄭若驊及其丈夫潘樂陶，在國外的資產、個人社交帳戶會否受影響向政府查詢，鄭若驊的聲明未有具體回應有關問題。<br />\n<br />\n她在聲明提到，與祖國和全國人民相比，個人利益毫不重要，為國家服務她感到自豪，維護國家安全之心亦堅定不移。 鄭若驊表示，維護國家安全是保障14億人民的生命安全和利益，並保障國家主權統一和領土完整，強調有機會為國家服務是她的光榮。"},{"pid":"dcab8747a5dcde64c9a036b19d72bf2b379ddc9d","tid":2146151,"uid":4575,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T11:44:45.000Z","msg":"老來乜都冇晒，得對波<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0eb6a79789d9d727672fc70886e4241f6075a91","tid":2146151,"uid":79563,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T11:45:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/54LFMqxguDE/maxresdefault.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2F54LFMqxguDE%2Fmaxresdefault.jpg&h=0282a506&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4253ee27552786106ffae52a13552b802a50f905","tid":2146151,"uid":279405,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,